happened in the first place.

00:17:08.190 --> 00:17:11.491 position:5% line:83% align:start
Man, you really are
a bad brother.

00:17:11.591 --> 00:17:13.926 position:16% line:89% align:start
You picking a fight with me?

00:17:14.960 --> 00:17:16.359 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I guess.

00:17:23.464 --> 00:17:25.398 position:16% line:83% align:start
Come on, you two!
What are you doing?!

00:17:25.498 --> 00:17:28.232 position:5% line:83% align:start
Please don't fight.
I've had enough!

00:17:38.405 --> 00:17:40.406 position:38% line:89% align:start
 You son of a bitch!

00:17:42.340 --> 00:17:43.607 position:5% line:89% align:start
Do you have any idea

00:17:43.707 --> 00:17:45.575 position:5% line:83% align:start
how much Mei has been suffering
because of you?!

00:17:45.675 --> 00:17:48.376 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're the one who's supposed
to be taking care of her!

00:17:50.811 --> 00:17:52.345 position:5% line:89% align:start
That's enough!

00:17:52.445 --> 00:17:53.812 position:27% line:83% align:start
You're Mei's brother,
aren't you?

00:17:53.912 --> 00:17:55.546 position:16% line:83% align:start
