her feelings for once!

00:17:55.646 --> 00:17:57.814 position:16% line:83% align:start
 -But I did!
 -Don't give me that!

00:17:57.914 --> 00:17:59.648 position:16% line:83% align:start
You little sister starts
sleeping with a guy like me

00:17:59.749 --> 00:18:01.382 position:16% line:83% align:start
and you don't do a damned
thing about it?

00:18:01.483 --> 00:18:02.751 position:16% line:89% align:start
