00:18:02.851 --> 00:18:04.718 position:5% line:89% align:start
Of course I was worried!

00:18:05.986 --> 00:18:08.221 position:16% line:83% align:start
Then why didn't you do
something about it, huh?!

00:18:08.320 --> 00:18:10.488 position:16% line:83% align:start
If you got an excuse,
I'm dying to hear it!

00:18:10.588 --> 00:18:12.856 position:5% line:83% align:start
I let it go it because
it was you, damn it!

00:18:12.956 --> 00:18:14.289 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [gasp]

00:18:15.656 --> 00:18:18.492 position:5% line:83% align:start
